      (hm_pos : 0 < m)
      (horder : analyticOrderAt f s = (m : вДХвИЮ))
      (hnotLocal : ¬ђ f =бґ†[рЭУЭ s] 0) :
      HasLogDerivPrincipalPart f s m

  theorem zetaLogDeriv_principalPart_at_nontrivial_zero
      {s : вДВ} (hs : IsNontrivialZetaZero s) :
      ZetaHasLogDerivPrincipalPart s

  theorem zetaLogDeriv_principalPart_at_one :
      HasLogDerivIntegerPrincipalPart riemannZeta (1 : вДВ) (-1)

Not declared yet вАФ would require ~50+ lines of analytic manipulation
proving each step.  The structural defs above suffice to *state* the
