    I.toClassicalInputs LC hT

/-! ### CW13: master theorem and `combine` refinement -/

/-- **CW13 вАФ MASTER FINAL THEOREM.**  Every structural, contour, RvM,
zero-classification, continuity, and good-height extension layer has
been discharged inside the file.  The headline bound
`|concreteS T| вЙ§ (1/2)¬Јlog T + 1/2` (for every `T вЙ• 140`) is now reduced
to exactly the **five sharp analytic inputs** packaged in
`BacklundSeparatedAnalyticInputs` together with the count discreteness
