### Phase 2 вАФ Complex analysis and final wiring (CXXXVIвАУCXXXVII)

**2.1 CXXXVI вАФ entire-function discharge.**

* Target: inhabit `EntireLocalPoleDecompositionHypothesis ќЮ`, i.e.
