  exact h_diff.analyticAt z

/-- в≠Р **PROVED вАФ `XiPullback` is non-degenerate at every UHP zero, given
non-triviality.** If `ќЮ` is not identically zero (witnessed by some
`ќЮ w вЙ† 0`), then no zero of `ќЮ` is the limit of an
identically-zero neighborhood, by the identity theorem on the
preconnected `вДВ` (Mathlib's
