/-- в≠Р **PROVED вАФ `EntireZeroFactorizationHypothesis XiPullback` from
regularity + non-triviality.** Composes:

* ¬І16.4 `entireAnalyticZerosAdmitFactorization_holds` (Mathlib
  isolated-zeros);
