/-- в≠Р **PROVED вАФ `completedHurwitzZetaEvenвВА 0` Schwarz, modulo the
FE-pair real-lifting target.** -/
theorem completedHurwitzZetaEvenвВА_zero_star
    (h_real : hurwitzEvenFEPair_zero_f_modif_ofReal_target) (s : вДВ) :
    HurwitzZeta.completedHurwitzZetaEvenвВА 0 (star s)
