/-- в≠Р **PROVED вАФ Schwarz reflection for `entireRiemannXi`, modulo the
FE-pair real-lifting target.** -/
theorem entireRiemannXi_schwarz_of_hurwitzZero
    (h_real : hurwitzEvenFEPair_zero_f_modif_ofReal_target) :
