/-- в≠Р **PROVED вАФ termwise comparison TвЖТ11/2 for the cloud denominator.**
For `12 вЙ§ T вЙ§ 13` and any `ќ≥`,
  `1/((11/2)¬≤ + ќ≥¬≤) вЙ§ 1/((T/2 - 1)¬≤ + ќ≥¬≤)`.
(The denominator on the right is positive since `T/2 - 1 вЙ• 5 > 0`.) -/
lemma one_div_Tbox_le_one_div_12_13
    {T ќ≥ : вДЭ}
    (hT12 : 12 вЙ§ T) (hT13 : T вЙ§ 13) :
    1 / (((11 / 2 : вДЭ)^2) + ќ≥^2)
