/-- в≠Р **PROVED вАФ Generic subband assembly for `[48, 80]`.**
Given closed-form bound by a constant `C`, cloud LB `K вЙ§ cloudK_T`,
tail LB `ѕД вЙ§ tailK_80_140 T`, and scalar margin `C вЙ§ 2 K + ѕД`,
closes the slab-cert inequality on the `x вЙ• 0` branch. -/
