/-- рЯМЯ **PROVED вАФ Finite-band regional anti-Herglotz from the two missing
analytic inputs.** Given the log-derivative decomposition and the
IBP-controlled error bound, the regional anti-Herglotz statement is
immediate by inlining `finiteBand_errorMargin_of_slabCD` + the model
anti-Herglotz fact + the decomposition. -/
theorem localXiPackage_10_140_regionAnti
    (error : вДВ вЖТ вДВ)
    (hdecomp : вИА z : вДВ,
        (вИГ T : вДЭ, 10 вЙ§ T вИІ T вЙ§ 140 вИІ
          2 * (1 + |z.re| + z.im) вЙ§ T) вЖТ
        logDerivativeResponse XiPullback z =
