-- ¬ІCCXIII. Model-parametric local package + ActualDensityTailData
-- =====================================================================
-- The previous ¬ІCCXII `localXiPackage_10_140_from_majorantBound`
-- (now `..._zeros100ceil`) hardcoded the dummy
-- `xiCloudDensityModel_zeros100ceil`. This section breaks that
-- coupling at the local-package layer:
--   вАҐ New `localXiPackage_10_140_from_majorantBound` is model-parametric:
--     it takes any `M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition`
