/-- рЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯ **PROVED вАФ MODEL-PARAMETRIC `LocalXiCloudDensityErrorPackage`
from a real majorant-primitive bound.**

Takes any `M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition` (with the standard
zeros-list compatibility + anti-Herglotz model), an IBP residual
`error`, the log-derivative decomposition `XiPullback = M.model + error`
on the `[10, 140]` adaptive region, and the majorant-primitive bound on
`|Im(error z)|`. Produces a `LocalXiCloudDensityErrorPackage`.

The dummy `xiCloudDensityModel_zeros100ceil` is no longer baked in;
any model satisfying the structural fields works. Routes through
`closedFormErrorControlled_of_majorantPrimitive_bound` + the existing
model-parametric `localPackage_10_140_of_slabCD`. -/
noncomputable def localXiPackage_10_140_from_majorantBound
    (M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition)
    (hM_zeros : M.zeros = zeros100ceil)
    (hmodelAnti : AntiHerglotzUHP M.model)
    (error : вДВ вЖТ вДВ)
    (hdecomp : вИА z : вДВ,
        (вИГ T : вДЭ, 10 вЙ§ T вИІ T вЙ§ 140 вИІ
          2 * (1 + |z.re| + z.im) вЙ§ T) вЖТ
        logDerivativeResponse XiPullback z = M.model z + error z)
    (hbound : вИА {z : вДВ} {T : вДЭ}, 10 вЙ§ T вЖТ T вЙ§ 140 вЖТ 0 < z.im вЖТ
              2 * (1 + |z.re| + z.im) вЙ§ T вЖТ
              |(error z).im| вЙ§
                -Phase1IBP.derivativeSideMajorantPrimitive
                  z.im (slabCD T).1 (slabCD T).2 T) :
    LocalXiCloudDensityErrorPackage :=
  localPackage_10_140_of_slabCD M hM_zeros hmodelAnti error hdecomp
    (closedFormErrorControlled_of_majorantPrimitive_bound error hbound)

/-- рЯУ¶ **`ActualDensityTailData`** вАФ future insertion point for the real
complex-valued density tail.

Packages everything `localXiPackage_10_140_from_majorantBound` needs:
the model `M` (with `zeros100ceil` + anti-Herglotz model), the IBP
residual `error`, the log-derivative decomposition, and the
majorant-primitive `|Im(error z)|` bound.

**Status:** abstract field-style structure. The real complex tail
integral
  `densityTail(z) = вИЂ u in T..вИЮ, pairedCauchyKernel u z dS(u)`
is *not* constructed here вАФ that requires complex-valued improper
integrals, real/imag-extraction commuting with limits, and the
complex kernel вЖФ `pairedCauchyImKernel` identity (separate task).
Once that lands, an inhabitant of this structure provides the
real-tail-instantiated `LocalXiCloudDensityErrorPackage` via
`localXiPackage_of_actualTailData` below. -/
structure ActualDensityTailData where
  /-- The density-tail model (eventually the real complex tail
  integral; for now any compatible `CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition`,
  including the dummy). -/
  M            : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition
  /-- Compatibility with the `zeros100ceil` finite-band setup. -/
  hM_zeros     : M.zeros = zeros100ceil
  /-- Anti-Herglotz model (upper-half-plane sign law). -/
  hmodelAnti   : AntiHerglotzUHP M.model
  /-- IBP residual error: `XiPullback = M.model + error` on `[10,140]`. -/
  error        : вДВ вЖТ вДВ
  /-- The log-derivative decomposition on the adaptive `[10,140]` region. -/
  hdecomp      :
    вИА z : вДВ,
      (вИГ T : вДЭ, 10 вЙ§ T вИІ T вЙ§ 140 вИІ 2 * (1 + |z.re| + z.im) вЙ§ T) вЖТ
      logDerivativeResponse XiPullback z = M.model z + error z
  /-- Majorant-primitive control on `|Im(error z)|`. -/
  hbound       :
    вИА {z : вДВ} {T : вДЭ}, 10 вЙ§ T вЖТ T вЙ§ 140 вЖТ 0 < z.im вЖТ
      2 * (1 + |z.re| + z.im) вЙ§ T вЖТ
      |(error z).im| вЙ§
        -Phase1IBP.derivativeSideMajorantPrimitive
          z.im (slabCD T).1 (slabCD T).2 T

/-- рЯМЯ **PROVED вАФ `LocalXiCloudDensityErrorPackage` from
`ActualDensityTailData`.** Convenience constructor: unpacks the
