-- ¬ІCCXVIII. Adaptive bound data + wrapper-kernel ActualDensityTailData
-- =====================================================================
-- Closes the wiring loop: adaptive convergence (¬ІCCXVII) plus the
-- finite-Im identity (¬ІCCXVI) plus real IBP data give an
-- `AdaptiveComplexTailIBPBoundData`, which produces the `hbound`
-- field, which feeds `ActualDensityTailData`, which feeds the
-- `LocalXiCloudDensityErrorPackage` via the ¬ІCCXIII model-parametric
-- theorem. Adds:
--
--   AdaptiveComplexTailIBPBoundData                вАФ adaptive Prop bundle
--   adaptiveComplexDensityTailFamilyPartial_im_tendsto
--   hbound_of_adaptiveComplexTailIBPBoundData      вАФ produces hbound
--   adaptiveComplexTailIBPBoundData_pairedDeriv    вАФ wrapper instantiation
--   actualDensityTailData_of_pairedDerivWrapper    вАФ full ActualDensityTailData
--   localXiPackage_of_pairedDerivWrapper           вАФ final local package
--
-- After this lands, the only remaining gap in the real-tail direction
