-- ¬ІCCXXX. atTop-oriented `TrueKernelTailDataAtTop` + concrete inhabitation
-- =====================================================================
-- Resolves the `T вЙ§ X` mismatch: the ¬ІCCXXVII / ¬ІCCXXVIII integrability
-- proofs require `T вЙ§ X`, but `TrueKernelTailData.true_int / wrap_int`
-- quantify over all `X`. Since improper tails only use `X вЖТ вИЮ`, we
-- introduce an atTop-oriented data structure and build the
-- `ActualDensityTailData` / capstone chain from it directly,
-- bypassing the unnatural `X < T` case.
