-- Adds:
--   TrueKernelTailDataAtTop                        вАФ atTop-oriented Type bundle
--   trueKernel_im_eq_realPartial_eventually        вАФ eventual Im match (atTop)
--   hbound_of_TrueKernelTailDataAtTop              вАФ produces hbound field
--   actualDensityTailData_of_trueKernelTailDataAtTop
--   localXiPackage_of_TrueKernelTailDataAtTop
--   trueKernelTailDataAtTop_of_finiteFluctuation   вАФ concrete instantiation
