/-- рЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯ **CLEAN FINAL FRONT DOOR (concrete model).**
End-to-end conditional capstone using:

* `hTuring` вАФ Turing/Backlund log envelope (parallel agent);
* concrete model: `us`, `M`, `hzeros`, `Tsmooth вЙ• 2ѕА`, `hmodel`
