-- ¬ІCCXLIII. Xi log-derivative formula pieces
-- =====================================================================
-- Splits the xi log-derivative decomposition into named sub-identities
-- matching the ¬ІCCXLII concrete front door. Produces both
-- `XiLogDerivativeDecompositionPieces` (¬ІCCXXXIV) and the matching
-- `herror` field in one bundle.
