-- Adds:
--   XiLogDerivativeFormulaPieces                      вАФ formula bundle
--   XiLogDerivativeDecompositionPieces.ofFormulaPieces вАФ conversion
--   XiActualTailDecompositionData.ofFormulaPieces      вАФ direct constructor
--   XiPullbackAntiHerglotzTarget_of_formulaPieces      вАФ final front door

/-- рЯУ¶ **`XiLogDerivativeFormulaPieces`** вАФ packaged xi log-derivative
identity layer. Wraps both `XiLogDerivativeDecompositionPieces`
(¬ІCCXXXIV) and the ¬ІCCXXXI `herror` Im-match into a single named
bundle, parameterized by the finite zero list `us`, the model
decomposition `M`, the smooth-tail base `Tsmooth`, and the residual
`error`.

Fields:
* `fluctTailPart` вАФ the residual fluctuation tail function;
* `model_eq` вАФ `M.model = finiteCloud + zeroDensity smooth tail`;
* `error_eq` вАФ `error = fluctTailPart`;
* `xi_formula` вАФ the headline identity
  `ќЫ[ќЮ] z = finiteCloud z + smoothTail z + fluctTail z` on adaptive band;
* `fluctTail_im_eq_trueTail` вАФ the constructed-tail Im match. -/
structure XiLogDerivativeFormulaPieces
    (Dzero : Phase1IBP.OrderedFluctuationMeasureData) (T0 : вДЭ)
    (hT0_pos : 0 < T0) (hT0_le_10 : T0 вЙ§ 10)
    (hTuring :
      вИА {z : вДВ} {T u : вДЭ},
        10 вЙ§ T вЖТ T вЙ§ 140 вЖТ 0 < z.im вЖТ
