Once a single inhabitant of this structure is produced, the front-door
theorem `XiPullbackAntiHerglotzTarget_of_XiLogDerivativeFormulaData`
closes everything. -/
structure XiLogDerivativeFormulaData
    (Dzero : Phase1IBP.OrderedFluctuationMeasureData) (T0 : вДЭ)
    (hT0_pos : 0 < T0) (hT0_le_10 : T0 вЙ§ 10)
    (hTuring :
      вИА {z : вДВ} {T u : вДЭ},
        10 вЙ§ T вЖТ T вЙ§ 140 вЖТ 0 < z.im вЖТ
        2 * (1 + |z.re| + z.im) вЙ§ T вЖТ
        T вЙ§ u вЖТ
        |Phase1IBP.finiteFluctuationPrimitive Dzero T0 u|
          вЙ§ (slabCD T).1 * Real.log u + (slabCD T).2)
    (us : List вДЭ)
