-- =====================================================================
-- ¬ІCCLXXVII. Low residual explicit-formula interface
-- =====================================================================
-- `Hlow` cannot be reduced to rational/log bounds alone:
-- `xiResidualError honestZeroDensityModelTwoPi` contains `ќЫ[ќЮ]` with
-- no concrete computation in the repo. The correct move is the
-- low-band analogue of `Hcanon_tailLimit` / `Hhigh_tailLimit`: a named
