/-- рЯУ¶ **`LowMarginDominatesExplicitBound`** вАФ model-margin side of
the split: the explicit residual bound is dominated by the actual
model margin on the compact low region. Tractable via `simpleCloudSum`
+ `HonestSmoothTailRationalLB_twoPi`. -/
def LowMarginDominatesExplicitBound
    (M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition) : Prop :=
  вИА z : вДВ,
    lowCompactRegion z вЖТ
    lowResidualExplicitBound z вЙ§ -(M.model z).im

/-- рЯМЯрЯМЯ **PROVED вАФ `XiLowResidualMargin` from the two-piece split.**
Composes the explicit residual bound (xi-specific) with the model
margin dominance (model-side analytic). -/
theorem XiLowResidualMargin_of_explicit_and_margin
    (Hexplicit : XiLowResidualExplicitData honestZeroDensityModelTwoPi)
    (Hmargin : LowMarginDominatesExplicitBound honestZeroDensityModelTwoPi) :
    XiLowResidualMargin honestZeroDensityModelTwoPi := by
