/-- **Parameterized low residual explicit bound** вАФ
`closedFormFirstZeroErrorBound` at user-supplied first-zero parameters
`(T, ќ≥вВБ, D)`. The ¬ІCCLXXVII constant-parameter `lowResidualExplicitBound`
is the `(2ѕА, 14, 1/2)` specialization (definitionally). -/
noncomputable def lowResidualExplicitBoundAt
    (T gamma1 D : вДЭ) (z : вДВ) : вДЭ :=
  closedFormFirstZeroErrorBound z.im T gamma1 D

/-- в≠Р **PROVED вАФ `lowResidualExplicitBound` is the `(2ѕА, 14, 1/2)`
specialization of the parameterized form.** -/
lemma lowResidualExplicitBound_eq_At (z : вДВ) :
    lowResidualExplicitBound z
      = lowResidualExplicitBoundAt (2 * Real.pi) 14 (1 / 2) z := rfl

/-- рЯУ¶ **`XiLowResidualExplicitDataAt T ќ≥вВБ D M`** вАФ parameterized
analogue of ¬ІCCLXXVII `XiLowResidualExplicitData`: on the compact low
region, the canonical residual's `Im` is bounded by the parameterized
explicit bound. -/
structure XiLowResidualExplicitDataAt
    (T gamma1 D : вДЭ)
    (M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition) : Prop where
  residual_bound :
    вИА z : вДВ,
      lowCompactRegion z вЖТ
      |(xiResidualError M z).im| вЙ§ lowResidualExplicitBoundAt T gamma1 D z

/-- рЯУ¶ **`LowMarginDominatesExplicitBoundAt T ќ≥вВБ D M`** вАФ
parameterized analogue of ¬ІCCLXXVII `LowMarginDominatesExplicitBound`. -/
def LowMarginDominatesExplicitBoundAt
    (T gamma1 D : вДЭ)
    (M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition) : Prop :=
  вИА z : вДВ,
