/-- рЯУ¶ **`LowExplicitArithmeticBoundAt T ќ≥вВБ D`** вАФ parameterized
analogue of ¬ІCCLXXVIII `LowExplicitArithmeticBound`. Pure arithmetic
inequality between the parameterized closed-form residual bound and
the model-side `simpleCloudSum + smoothTailRationalLowerBoundAbs(...,10)`
lower bound. The smooth inner cutoff is fixed at `10`, the forced
