-- trick (which used `5/ѕА < 2`) by the tangent-line bound
-- `log(q) вЙ§ log 2 + q/2 вИТ 1` (obtained from
-- `Real.log_le_sub_one_of_pos` applied to `q/2`), valid for any `q > 0`,
-- which is sharper near `q = 2`. Numerical margin to `1/2`: вЙИ 0.068.
