/-- рЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯ **PROVED вАФ guarded high `LocalXiCloudDensityErrorPackage`
from guarded `XiHighResidualFormulaDataAwayFromZeros`.** -/
noncomputable def highLocalPackage_of_XiHighResidualFormulaDataAwayFromZeros
    (Dzero : Phase1IBP.OrderedFluctuationMeasureData) (T0 : вДЭ)
    (hT0_pos : 0 < T0) (hT0_le_140 : T0 вЙ§ 140)
    (M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition)
