-- ¬ІCCLXXXV. xi residual вЖФ bounded low IBP вАФ final analytic bridge
-- =====================================================================
-- ¬ІCCLXXXIV built the bounded low IBP estimates:
--   `|boundary| вЙ§ 8yD/T¬≤`,
--   `|deriv side| вЙ§ 9yD/T¬≤ вИТ 9yD/ќ≥¬≤`,
--   `|boundary| + |deriv side| вЙ§ closedFormFirstZeroErrorBound y T ќ≥ D`.
-- The remaining xi-side step is identifying the residual with (or
-- dominating it by) these finite IBP pieces:
--   `|Im(xiResidualError honestZeroDensityModelTwoPi z)|
--     вЙ§ |lowFirstZeroBoundaryTerm ... 11| + |lowFirstZeroDerivativeSide ... 11 14|`.
--
-- This section names that identification as `XiLowResidualFiniteIBPDomination`
-- (the substantive xi explicit-formula step), names the supporting
-- `S = -NвВА` identity as `FirstZeroGapForDzero`, and proves the mechanical
-- closure that turns these two Props (plus integrability of `|S¬Јk'|` on
-- `[11, 14]`) into the ¬ІCCLXXXIII `XiResidualLowIBPRepresentationAt`.
--
-- Adds:
--   XiLowResidualFiniteIBPDomination                      вАФ residual вЙ§ |boundary| + |deriv|
--   FirstZeroGapForDzero                                  вАФ S = -NвВА on first-zero gap
--   finiteFluctuation_abs_le_half_on_11_14                вАФ |S| вЙ§ 1/2 on [11, 14]
--   XiResidualLowIBPRepresentationAt_11_14_half_of_finiteIBP
--                                                         вАФ mechanical closure
--   XiPullbackAntiHerglotzTarget_of_twoPiModel_lowFiniteIBP_11_14_half
--                                                         вАФ final front door

/-- рЯУ¶ **`XiLowResidualFiniteIBPDomination`** вАФ the xi explicit-formula
identification: on the compact low region, the canonical residual's `Im`
is dominated by the bounded-IBP boundary + derivative pieces at the
canonical first-zero cutoffs `T = 11`, `ќ≥ = 14`. This isolates the
**xi-side analytic content** from the already-proved IBP estimates. -/
structure XiLowResidualFiniteIBPDomination
    (Dzero : Phase1IBP.OrderedFluctuationMeasureData) (T0 : вДЭ)
    (M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition) : Prop where
  residual_le_finite_ibp :
    вИА z : вДВ,
      lowCompactRegion z вЖТ
      |(xiResidualError M z).im|
        вЙ§ |lowFirstZeroBoundaryTerm Dzero T0 z.re z.im 11|
          + |lowFirstZeroDerivativeSide Dzero T0 z.re z.im 11 14|

/-- рЯУ¶ **`FirstZeroGapForDzero Dzero T0 ќ≥`** вАФ first-zero-gap identity
