-- Proves `smoothLBConst вЙ§ smoothTailRationalLowerBoundAbsNorm z.re z.im 10`
-- where `smoothLBConst := (259/3586)¬Ј(5/29) вЙИ 0.01246`. The factor
-- `5/29` is the uniform LB for the kernel factor (equality at `(0, 4)`);
-- `259/3586` is the rational LB for `ѕБ(10)` via Pad√© `log(5/ѕА) вЙ• 74/163`
