/-- рЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯ **PATH B
FINAL FRONT DOOR (Hadamard source + independent Stieltjes tail/low)**.

Path B is now in its most decomposed form: four genuinely
distinguishable analytic inputs, plus the parallel-agent log envelopes
and trivial data-side gap.

```
hTuring + hHighLog                                 (parallel agent вАФ log envelopes)
+ Hsrc  : XiHadamardLogDerivativeSource             (A: Hadamard product log-deriv)
+ Htail : StieltjesTailContributionData ... ZC      (B1: tail Stieltjes split)
+ Hlow  : StieltjesLowContributionData ... ZC       (B2: low finite Stieltjes split)
+ h_Z_ge_15                                          (trivial)
вЯє XiPullbackAntiHerglotzTarget
```

B1 (tail) and B2 (low) can be attacked independently. -/
theorem XiPullbackAntiHerglotzTarget_of_twoPiModel_hadamardAndStieltjesTailLow
    (Dzero : Phase1IBP.OrderedFluctuationMeasureData)
    (h_Z_ge_15 : вИА i : вДХ, (15 : вДЭ) вЙ§ Dzero.toFluctuationMeasureData.Z i)
    (hTuring :
      вИА {z : вДВ} {T u : вДЭ},
        10 вЙ§ T вЖТ T вЙ§ 140 вЖТ 0 < z.im вЖТ
        2 * (1 + |z.re| + z.im) вЙ§ T вЖТ
        T вЙ§ u вЖТ
        |Phase1IBP.finiteFluctuationPrimitive Dzero 10 u|
          вЙ§ (slabCD T).1 * Real.log u + (slabCD T).2)
    (hHighLog :
      вИА {z : вДВ} {T u : вДЭ},
        140 вЙ§ T вЖТ 0 < z.im вЖТ
        2 * (1 + |z.re| + z.im) вЙ§ T вЖТ
        T вЙ§ u вЖТ
        |Phase1IBP.finiteFluctuationPrimitive Dzero 10 u|
          вЙ§ (1 / 2 : вДЭ) * Real.log u + (49 / 20 : вДЭ))
    (Hsrc : XiHadamardLogDerivativeSource)
    (Htail : StieltjesTailContributionData Dzero 10 Hsrc.zeroContribution)
    (Hlow : StieltjesLowContributionData Dzero 10 Hsrc.zeroContribution) :
    XiPullbackAntiHerglotzTarget :=
  XiPullbackAntiHerglotzTarget_of_twoPiModel_hadamardAndStieltjesFormula
    Dzero h_Z_ge_15 hTuring hHighLog Hsrc
    (ZeroContributionStieltjesFormula_of_tail_low_data Htail Hlow)

-- =====================================================================
-- ¬ІCCCX. Regional tail Stieltjes data + bridge bypassing global form
-- =====================================================================
-- `StieltjesTailContributionData` and `XiModelTailExplicitFormula` are
-- region-agnostic вАФ they quantify over ALL `T` with `regime`, including
-- small `T` where convergence may require non-existent log envelopes.
-- The actual consumers only need mid (`T = canonicalAdaptiveT z` with
-- `10 вЙ§ T вЙ§ 140`) and high (`T вЙ• 140`).
--
-- This section adds the regional Props (`XiMidHighTailExplicitFormula`,
-- `StieltjesMidHighTailContributionData`), bridges them through to the
-- corrected-split front door, and separates equality from convergence
-- so the Stieltjes equality theorem doesn't have to re-prove convergence
-- already covered by `trueKernelComplexTail_converges_at_of_logEnvelope`.

/-- рЯУ¶ **`XiMidHighTailExplicitFormula`** вАФ regional analogue of
`XiModelTailExplicitFormula`. Covers mid (at `canonicalAdaptiveT z`)
and high (`T вЙ• 140`) only вАФ matches actual use cases. -/
structure XiMidHighTailExplicitFormula
    (Dzero : Phase1IBP.OrderedFluctuationMeasureData) (T0 : вДЭ)
    (M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition) : Prop where
  mid_formula :
    вИА {z : вДВ},
      0 < z.im вЖТ
      (вИГ T : вДЭ, 10 вЙ§ T вИІ T вЙ§ 140 вИІ
        2 * (1 + |z.re| + z.im) вЙ§ T) вЖТ
      вИГ L : вДВ,
        XiFluctuationTailValue Dzero T0 (canonicalAdaptiveT z) z L вИІ
        logDerivativeResponse XiPullback z = M.model z + L
  high_formula :
    вИА {z : вДВ} {T : вДЭ},
      140 вЙ§ T вЖТ
      0 < z.im вЖТ
      2 * (1 + |z.re| + z.im) вЙ§ T вЖТ
      вИГ L : вДВ,
        XiFluctuationTailValue Dzero T0 T z L вИІ
        logDerivativeResponse XiPullback z = M.model z + L

/-- рЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯ **PROVED вАФ bridge from regional formula to
`XiLogDerivativeModelTailDecomposition`.** Direct unpacking of the
mid/high fields. Bypasses the over-strong global
`XiModelTailExplicitFormula`. -/
theorem XiLogDerivativeModelTailDecomposition_of_midHighTailFormula
    {Dzero : Phase1IBP.OrderedFluctuationMeasureData} {T0 : вДЭ}
    {M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition}
    (H : XiMidHighTailExplicitFormula Dzero T0 M) :
    XiLogDerivativeModelTailDecomposition Dzero T0 M := by
  refine вЯ®?_, ?_вЯ©
  ¬Ј intro z T hT hy hr
    obtain вЯ®L, hL, hdвЯ© := H.high_formula hT hy hr
    exact вЯ®L, hL.tendsto_tail, hdвЯ©
  ¬Ј intro z hy hm
    obtain вЯ®L, hL, hdвЯ© := H.mid_formula hy hm
    exact вЯ®L, hL.tendsto_tail, hdвЯ©

/-- рЯУ¶ **`StieltjesMidHighTailContributionData`** вАФ regional Stieltjes
