/-- рЯМЯрЯМЯрЯМЯ **PROVED вАФ `XiMidHighTailExplicitFormula` from Hadamard
source + regional Stieltjes data** (at the honest twoPi model). -/
theorem XiMidHighTailExplicitFormula_of_hadamardSource_and_midHighTailData
    {Dzero : Phase1IBP.OrderedFluctuationMeasureData} {T0 : вДЭ}
    (Hsrc : XiHadamardLogDerivativeSource)
    (Htail :
      StieltjesMidHighTailContributionData
        Dzero T0 Hsrc.zeroContribution) :
    XiMidHighTailExplicitFormula
