* `tail_exact`  вАФ the abstract tail contribution equals
  `lowTailZeroContribution Dzero T0 z`. The `XiPullback z вЙ† 0` and
  `LowFirstZeroGapNoAtoms Dzero` guards are inherited from the target.
* `split`       вАФ `ZC z = finiteCloud z + tail z` on the low compact
  region under the same guards.

