-- =====================================================================

/-- в≠Р **PROVED вАФ algebra for the ќЊ correction term**, valid for
`s вЙ† 0` and `s вЙ† 1`. The identity fails at s = 0 and s = 1 in Lean's
totalized arithmetic (`1/0 = 0`), because the `+ 1/2` correction
